    "title": "Kifo",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "kifo",
    "language": "swh",
    "content": "<p>Binadamu ni wenye kufa, na kifo ni mwisho wa kawaida wa maisha duniani (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps90:1-Ps90:6\">Zaburi 90:1–6</a>). Utambulisho wa binadamu ulianza wakati Mungu alipovuta pumzi ya uhai kwenye mavumbi ya dunia na kumuumba Adamu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen2:7\">Mwanzo 2:7</a>). Hali hii inarudi wakati wa kifo Mungu anapochukua pumzi yake. Kisha mwili wa binadamu unarudi mavumbini (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:19\">3:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job4:19-Job4:21\">Ayubu 4:19–21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:6-Isa40:8\">Isaya 40:6–8</a>). Maisha ya binadamu yanategemea kikamilifu muumba. Pumzi yake ni zawadi inayotutegemeza mradi tu anaruhusu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps104:29\">Zaburi 104:29</a>).</p><p>Dhambi ilileta kifo katika maisha ya binadamu na kusababisha madhara makubwa. Kifo mara nyingi huja bila onyo, na huwafanya watu wahisi huzuni kubwa. Wakati mtu anapokufa, inaweza kuhisi kama matumaini na mipango yao ya siku zijazo imefikia mwisho. Adhabu ya kifo ndiyo adhabu kali zaidi ambayo mahakama za kibinadamu zinaweza kutoa. Katika Agano la Kale, adhabu ya kifo ilikuwa kwa mauaji au kufuru (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen9:6\">Mwanzo 9:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod21:12\">Kutoka 21:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev24:16\">Mambo ya Walawi 24:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:30-John10:33\">Yohana 10:30–33</a>). Haya yalikuwa makosa ambayo yaliweka jamii katika hatari.</p><p>Kwenye Agano la Kale, <em>Sheol</em> ni kinyume cha &quot;nchi ya walio hai&quot; (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps27:13\">Zaburi 27:13</a>). Hapa ni mahali pa giza na kimya ambapo wafu wanakaa (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job10:21-Job10:22\">Ayubu 10:21–22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps94:17\">Zaburi 94:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah2:6\">Yona 2:6</a>). Hata katika kifo, watu wa Mungu wana tumaini (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov14:32\">Mithali 14:32</a>). Mungu ni mkuu, ana udhibiti kamili na anatawala juu ya kifo (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:39\">Kumbukumbu la Torati 32:39</a>).</p><p>Agano la Kale mara nyingi linaelezea kifo kama kujiunga na mababu, bila kutaja ufufuo (tazama, kwa mfano, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen49:29-Gen49:33\">Mwanzo 49:29–33</a>). Hata hivyo, kuna ishara za ufufuo (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job19:25-Job19:27\">Ayubu 19:25–27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa25:6-Isa25:9\">Isaiah 25:6–9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa26:19\">26:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan12:2\">Danieli 12:2</a>). Imani ya Kiyahudi kuhusu ufufuo ilianza kuwa ya kawaida zaidi katika kipindi kati ya Agano la Kale na Jipya.</p><p>Ufufuo ni mada kuu katika Agano Jipya. Kupitia Kristo, watu wa Mungu waliokombolewa watashinda kifo. Kifo ni adui wa mwisho ambaye Mungu ataangamiza (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:54-1Cor15:57\">1 Wakorintho 15:54–57, </a><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:26\">26</a>). Kifo kinatokana na dhambi (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:12\">Warumi 5:12</a>). Wale wanaoishi katika hali ya dhambi na hawatubu (yaani, kugeuka kutoka dhambi) watapata adhabu katika ziwa la moto, linalojulikana kama &quot;kifo cha pili&quot; (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:8\">Ufunuo 21:8</a>).</p><p>Lakini kifo cha Yesu kilishinda kifo. Yesu alipokufa na kufufuka tena, alionyesha kwamba kifo si mamlaka ya mwisho juu ya wanadamu. Ufufuo wake ni mfano kwa Wakristo wote (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:18\">Wakolosai 1:18</a>). Yeye ni &quot;Bwana wa walio hai na wafu&quot; (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom14:9\">Warumi 14:9</a>). Mtu anapokufa, ni kawaida kuomboleza. Hata hivyo, pia inapaswa kuwa wakati wa kuonyesha imani kubwa kwa Mungu. Wale wanaopokea ahadi za Mungu wana tumaini kwamba wataishi baada ya kaburi.</p><p><u>Sehemu za Kujifunza Zaidi</u></p><p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen2:15-Gen2:17\">Mwanzo 2:15–17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:19\">3:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen6:17\">6:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen9:5-Gen9:6\">9:5–6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen49:29-Gen49:33\">49:29–33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod21:12-Exod21:17\">Kutoka 21:12–17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod21:28-Exod21:29\">28–29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod23:7\">23:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod31:14-Exod31:15\">31:14–15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev24:16\">Mambo ya Walawi 24:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:39\">Kumbukumbu la Torati 32:39</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job10:18-Job10:22\">Ayubu 10:18–22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job19:25-Job19:27\">19:25–27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps90:1-Ps90:12\">Zaburi 90:1–12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps94:17\">94:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov14:32\">Mithali 14:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl12:1-Eccl12:7\">Mhubiri 12:1–7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa25:6-Isa25:9\">Isaya 25:6–9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa26:19\">26:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:6-Isa40:8\">40:6–8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan12:2-Dan12:3\">Danieli 12:2–3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:26-Mark12:27\">Marko 12:26–27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:12-Rom5:17\">Warumi 5:12–17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:20-1Cor15:26\">1 Wakorintho 15:20–26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:51-1Cor15:58\">51–58</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev20:4-Rev20:6\">Ufunuo 20:4–6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev20:11-Rev20:15\">11–15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:3-Rev21:8\">21:3–8</a></p>",
